{"tid":490009,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"E-Kids打不死！懶理負評殺入日本娛樂圈","createTime":"2017-12-05T09:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T16:43:15.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ac4fd3ce35544618acabeae7b3f9e44402a776a4","tid":490009,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T09:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171204/photo/bkn-20171204221358244-1204_00862_001_02p.jpg?20171204231617\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171204%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171204221358244-1204_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20171204231617&h=b09a9597&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「MK Pop始祖」E-Kids喺年初合體開騷，仲推出新歌，當時佢哋話拍攝新歌MV用咗六位數字嘅資金！不過一班網民都話淨係見到個鏡頭不停360度轉，真係睇到頭暈兼想嘔。雖然劣評如潮，但E-kids一於少理，仲喺今日發布佢哋攻日嘅消息！ <br />\n<br />\n今日E-Kids嘅官方Facebook專頁就上載咗兩張日文嘅新聞稿：「我哋首張Digital EP E-Kids Again 1234 japan edition即將會喺12月13號喺日本正式上架，入面會有三首全新廣東歌曲同埋一首kukatachii remix！見到呢份全日文嘅official press release實在係太夢幻啦！之後我哋會再補條正式嘅訂購連結，到時如果大家有興趣，都可以喺香港購買支持下我哋嘗試發展日本市場嘅第一步！我哋會努力！二月嘅演唱會，我哋喺日内會公布賣飛詳情㗎喇，大家請稍等多一陣。」 <br />\n<br />\n新聞稿入面仲以「香港人氣男子組合」去形容E-Kids，仲有眼利網民發現篇新聞稿將成員郁禮賢（Tim）同林詠倫（Alan）掉轉咗，E-Kids佢哋都忍唔住留言自抽：「哈哈，可能日本朋友覺得Alan個樣襯阿Tim個名多啲，阿Tim個樣又襯Alan個名多啲。」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171204/mobile/bkn-20171204221358244-1204_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171204%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20171204221358244-1204_00862_001.html&d=VMaFsTKRgPB3rgaWfNMaJKS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=12c1400c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171204/mobile/bkn-20171204221358244-1204_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3839c041b39f14bada7d2c80a972d43399d6d597","tid":490009,"uid":146893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T09:08:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樂壇小強"},{"pid":"